OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBrazil bans the sale of    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FiPhones without chargers   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Brazil says it is banning the sale of  
OL,6, iPhones which do not include a power   
OL,7, adapter.                               
OL,9,FIn a statement on Tuesday, Brazil's    
OL,10,FMinistry of Justice and Public Security
OL,11,Fsaid it has fined Apple 12.275 million 
OL,12,Freais (#2.04m).                        
OL,14,FBrazilian consumer agency Senacon said 
OL,15,FApple's decision not to include power  
OL,16,Fadapters with new iPhones discriminates
OL,17,Fagainst consumers by selling an        
OL,18,F"incomplete product".                  
OL,20,FApple will appeal against the ban.     
